---
/**
 * About page (/about) — Nuro's mission statement. A single prose column on
 * the cream surface, sharing the Nav/Footer shell with the rest of the site.
 * Copy supplied verbatim by the team (English mission statement).
 */
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "@/components/nav/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/footer/Footer.astro";
import Reveal from "@/components/motion/Reveal.astro";
import styles from "@/components/about/about.module.css";

// Static page (the server adapter stays for the API routes).
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="About — Nuro"
  description="Nuro's mission: help every school give neurodivergent students the adapted support the law says they're entitled to — before they fall through the cracks."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <section class={styles.section}>
      <div class={styles.container}>
        <Reveal as="span" eager class={styles.eyebrow}>About</Reveal>
        <Reveal as="h1" eager delay={0.06} class={styles.heading}>
          Nuro mission statement
        </Reveal>

        <div class={styles.body}>
          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.12}>
            The law says it clearly: every student has the right to adapted
            support. But that&rsquo;s also where the system ends.
          </Reveal>

          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.16}>
            Millions of neurodivergent students in schools where there&rsquo;s
            no room for them. Where educators don&rsquo;t have the tools. Where
            budgets are already exhausted. Where a student with ADHD, autism or
            dyslexia &ndash; who just needed the right support at the right time
            &ndash; so no one is at risk of becoming a school refuser.
          </Reveal>

          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.2} class={styles.lede}>
            It&rsquo;s not a design issue. It&rsquo;s a system failure.
          </Reveal>

          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.24}>
            We built Nuro to change that.
          </Reveal>

          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.28}>
            We enable educators to see every individual student &ndash; to
            provide the personalized support that the law says students are
            entitled to. We catch students at risk of falling between the lines
            long before they become homeschoolers. We help every student
            develop their superpowers while supporting them with their
            challenges.
          </Reveal>

          <Reveal as="p" delay={0.32} class={styles.closer}>
            The law was right. The system only needed one tool &ndash; and now
            it&rsquo;s here!
          </Reveal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
